languages.text: "Гончие Кикеросс мертвы! Мы показали себя, может, культ даже возьмет нас под покровительство! Вот только нас... слишком много. А много победителей не бывает!"

traits.locale_text: [Драфт] Теперь настал твой черед, Вольный Торговец

languages.text: "Keykeross's hounds are dead! We've proven ourselves. Maybe the Cult will even take us under their protection! But there are... too many of us. And there can't be too many winners!"

languages.text: « Les limiers de Keykeross sont morts ! Nous avons fait nos preuves. Peut-être que le culte acceptera de nous prendre sous son aile ! Mais nous sommes... encore trop nombreux. Et il ne faut pas qu'il y ait trop de vainqueurs ! »

languages.text: “绮克萝丝的猎犬已经死了！我们已经证明了力量，说不定巫灵教派会保护我们！不过……我们活着的人太多了，他们不可能允许有这么多赢家！”
languages.original_text: "Keykeross's hounds are dead! We've proven ourselves. Maybe the Cult will even take us under their protection! But there are... too many of us. And there can't be too many winners!"

languages.text: 「キーケロスの猟犬が死んだぞ！俺たちの力を示せたんだ。これで魔女団が俺たちを保護してくれるかもしれない！だが…俺たちは数が多すぎる。勝者の数も多すぎるぞ！」
languages.original_text: "Keykeross's hounds are dead! We've proven ourselves. Maybe the Cult will even take us under their protection! But there are... too many of us. And there can't be too many winners!"

languages.text: "Keykeross' Hunde sind tot! Wir haben uns gut geschlagen. Vielleicht wird uns der Kult sogar unter seinen Schutz nehmen! Aber ... wir sind zu viele. Und es darf nicht zu viele Sieger geben!"
languages.original_text: "Keykeross's hounds are dead! We've proven ourselves. Maybe the Cult will even take us under their protection! But there are... too many of us. And there can't be too many winners!"

languages.text: «¡Los perros de Keykeross están muertos! Hemos demostrado nuestra valía. ¡Incluso puede que ahora el culto nos tome bajo su protección! Pero... somos demasiados. ¡Y no puede haber demasiados vencedores!».

languages.text: "Keykeross'un itleri nalları dikti! Kendimizi kanıtladık. Tarikat bizi kanatları altına alabilir! Ancak... Sayımız çok fazla. Bu kadar fazla galip olamaz!"
